    • Constructor Detail

      • RenameMethodAdapter

        public RenameMethodAdapter(MethodVisitor mv)
        Creates a method visitor that renames all references from a given old name to a given new name. The method visitor will also rename all inner classes. The names must be full qualified internal ASM names (e.g. com/blah/MyClass$InnerClass).
